3, Brazzel 0-2 0-3 0, Reede 0-2 0-0 0. Totals 19-61 8-20 46.
</P>
<P>
   ARIZONA STATE _ Newman 4-6 3-4 12, Sand 6-10 2-2 15, Holt 4-9
