<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-31 09:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3187 &Cx1f; tab-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NYTBOOK-MOVIE-1000&AMP;AD     12-31 1537
