<P>
   NAMES (San Francisco) _ Move over Andrew and Megan. Here come
Madison, Tyler and Alexis. And don't even try to mess with Michael.
Among American parents favorite names for newborns in 1998, Michael
was the most popular _ for the 35th year in a row. Kaitlyn
reclaimed its No.1 spot for girls after being bumped out of that
position by Sarah last year. By MARSHA GINSBURG.
