gilt doors Jan. 5 for the first time in four years, old-timers will
recognize the place _ bits of it. But many things have changed
after its renovation. Still, the 1915 French Renaissance-style
building is considered by many experts to be San Francisco's most
beautiful structure. By GERALD D. ADAMS.
