<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-31 15:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3663 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FREEDOM-RIDER-4TAKES-     12-31 1330
