<HEADLINE>
KEY RATES 
</HEADLINE>
  (th) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the daily key rates from The New York Times.
</P>
<P>
   -------------------Thursday----Previous day---Year Ago
</P>
<P>
   PRIME RATE ---------- 7.75 ------ 7.75 ------- 8.50
</P>
<P>
   DISCOUNT RATE ------- 4.50 ------ 4.50 ------- 5.00
</P>
<P>
   FEDERAL FUNDS(x) ---- 5.00 ------ 4.80 ------- 5.84
</P>
<P>
