Fridays, to 8:30 p.m. Admission; $9.50; $6.50 for students and the
elderly.
</P>
<P>
   NEW-YORK HISTORICAL SOCIETY, 2 West 77th St., (212) 873-3400.
Hours: Tuesdays through Sundays, 11 a.m. to 5 p.m.; closed Jan. 1.
Admission: $5; $3 for students and the elderly; free for children
under 12.
</P>
