</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WHAT-NEXT-IRAQ?-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CAUGHT BETWEEN IRAQ AND A HARD PLACE  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This excellent 850-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning Jan. 2, 1999 _ Happy New Year!) Economist
magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
